Hello everybody,

i'm pleased to announce the release 0.5pre of Cameleon,
my OCaml-oriented development environment.

Changes are (from Cameleon's change log):
  * config directory is now ~/.cameleon instead of ~/.cameleonrc,
  * all menus can be configured,
  * support for plug-ins: put the .cmo plugins files in your ~/.cameleon/plugins directory (see plugins/*.ml for examples),
  * commands can be shell commands (beginning with '#') or cameleon internal commands,
  * new ocamldoc generators (odoc_command.cmo and odoc_command_latex.cmo) added to create plug-ins documentation,
  * manual update.

http://www.maxence-g.net/Tools/cameleon/cameleon.html

Enjoy !

--
Maxence Guesdon

